column5: Nothing Special photo wise, just my dog and the Rose of Sharon bushes covered in snow for the first time this year!         Happy New Years to all..Now bring on the ice PLEASE!!!!
Beautiful husky ! We had snow here yesterda, but most of it melted last night with the 25mm of rain we got.Now its a skating rink with the flash freeze we had this morning.
Nice looking Pup! Here are a few shots out the kitchen window today. It is still snowing and -9, so it should be around for a bit!
ahhh... Snow.... the other white drug
